            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EEzekiel%2021%3A1-22%3A31%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_1%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEzekiel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22subhead-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Sword%20of%20Judgment%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E21%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Verses%2021%3A1-32%20are%20numbered%2021%3A6-37%20in%20Hebrew%20text.%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20this%20message%20came%20to%20me%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_2%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%20turn%20and%20face%20Jerusalem%20and%20prophesy%20against%20Israel%20and%20her%20sanctuaries.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_3%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ETell%20her%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20I%20am%20your%20enemy%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3BIsrael%2C%20and%20I%20am%20about%20to%20unsheath%20my%20sword%20to%20destroy%20your%20people%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20righteous%20and%20the%20wicked%20alike.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_4%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EYes%2C%20I%20will%20cut%20off%20both%20the%20righteous%20and%20the%20wicked!%20I%20will%20draw%20my%20sword%20against%20everyone%20in%20the%20land%20from%20south%20to%20north.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_5%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EEveryone%20in%20the%20world%20will%20know%20that%20I%20am%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20My%20sword%20is%20in%20my%20hand%2C%20and%20it%20will%20not%20return%20to%20its%20sheath%20until%20its%20work%20is%20finished.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_6%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%20groan%20before%20the%20people!%20Groan%20before%20them%20with%20bitter%20anguish%20and%20a%20broken%20heart.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_7%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20they%20ask%20why%20you%20are%20groaning%2C%20tell%20them%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BI%20groan%20because%20of%20the%20terrifying%20news%20I%20have%20heard.%20When%20it%20comes%20true%2C%20the%20boldest%20heart%20will%20melt%20with%20fear%3B%20all%20strength%20will%20disappear.%20Every%20spirit%20will%20faint%3B%20strong%20knees%20will%20become%20as%20weak%20as%20water.%20And%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20It%20is%20coming!%20It%26%23x2019%3Bs%20on%20its%20way!%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_8%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_9%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%20give%20the%20people%20this%20message%20from%20the%20Lord%3A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BA%20sword%2C%20a%20sword%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eis%20being%20sharpened%20and%20polished.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_10%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20is%20sharpened%20for%20terrible%20slaughter%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20polished%20to%20flash%20like%20lightning!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ENow%20will%20you%20laugh%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EThose%20far%20stronger%20than%20you%20have%20fallen%20beneath%20its%20power!%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E21%3A10%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20meaning%20of%20the%20Hebrew%20is%20uncertain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_11%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EYes%2C%20the%20sword%20is%20now%20being%20sharpened%20and%20polished%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eit%20is%20being%20prepared%20for%20the%20executioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_12%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%20cry%20out%20and%20wail%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Epound%20your%20thighs%20in%20anguish%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Efor%20that%20sword%20will%20slaughter%20my%20people%20and%20their%20leaders%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eeveryone%20will%20die!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_13%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20will%20put%20them%20all%20to%20the%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EWhat%20chance%20do%20they%20have%3F%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E21%3A13%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20meaning%20of%20the%20Hebrew%20is%20uncertain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Esays%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_14%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%20prophesy%20to%20them%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20clap%20your%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThen%20take%20the%20sword%20and%20brandish%20it%20twice%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eeven%20three%20times%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Eto%20symbolize%20the%20great%20massacre%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethe%20great%20massacre%20facing%20them%20on%20every%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_15%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3ELet%20their%20hearts%20melt%20with%20terror%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Efor%20the%20sword%20glitters%20at%20every%20gate.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EIt%20flashes%20like%20lightning%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20is%20polished%20for%20slaughter!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_16%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EO%26%23xA0%3Bsword%2C%20slash%20to%20the%20right%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethen%20slash%20to%20the%20left%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Ewherever%20you%20will%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewherever%20you%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_17%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EI%2C%20too%2C%20will%20clap%20my%20hands%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20I%20will%20satisfy%20my%20fury.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EI%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20have%20spoken!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_18%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EOmens%20for%20Babylon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20King%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20this%20message%20came%20to%20me%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_19%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%20make%20a%20map%20and%20trace%20two%20routes%20on%20it%20for%20the%20sword%20of%20Babylon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20king%20to%20follow.%20Put%20a%20signpost%20on%20the%20road%20that%20comes%20out%20of%20Babylon%20where%20the%20road%20forks%20into%20two%26%23x2014%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_20%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3Eone%20road%20going%20to%20Ammon%20and%20its%20capital%2C%20Rabbah%2C%20and%20the%20other%20to%20Judah%20and%20fortified%20Jerusalem.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_21%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%20of%20Babylon%20now%20stands%20at%20the%20fork%2C%20uncertain%20whether%20to%20attack%20Jerusalem%20or%20Rabbah.%20He%20calls%20his%20magicians%20to%20look%20for%20omens.%20They%20cast%20lots%20by%20shaking%20arrows%20from%20the%20quiver.%20They%20inspect%20the%20livers%20of%20animal%20sacrifices.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_22%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20omen%20in%20his%20right%20hand%20says%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BJerusalem!%26%23x2019%3B%20With%20battering%20rams%20his%20soldiers%20will%20go%20against%20the%20gates%2C%20shouting%20for%20the%20kill.%20They%20will%20put%20up%20siege%20towers%20and%20build%20ramps%20against%20the%20walls.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_23%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20people%20of%20Jerusalem%20will%20think%20it%20is%20a%20false%20omen%2C%20because%20of%20their%20treaty%20with%20the%20Babylonians.%20But%20the%20king%20of%20Babylon%20will%20remind%20the%20people%20of%20their%20rebellion.%20Then%20he%20will%20attack%20and%20capture%20them.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_24%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BTherefore%2C%20this%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20Again%20and%20again%20you%20remind%20me%20of%20your%20sin%20and%20your%20guilt.%20You%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20even%20try%20to%20hide%20it!%20In%20everything%20you%20do%2C%20your%20sins%20are%20obvious%20for%20all%20to%20see.%20So%20now%20the%20time%20of%20your%20punishment%20has%20come!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_21_25%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2221%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3Byou%20corrupt%2